  "content": "\n    <span class=\"highlight-purple\">A Lab Bench.</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"slide-subtitle\" style=\"font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n    Observe, hypothesize, change, measure. All through MCP.<br>\n    All without leaving the conversation.\n  </div>\n  <!-- The loop -->\n  <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n    <div class=\"card\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-cyan); padding: 20px 24px;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 15px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-cyan); min-width: 28px;\">1</div>\n        <div>\n          <div style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;\">Observe</div>\n          <div style=\"font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 4px;\">Traces show retrieval is 60-85% of RAG latency. Graph expansion adds significant cost.</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"card\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-amber); padding: 20px 24px;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 15px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-amber); min-width: 28px;\">2</div>\n        <div>\n          <div style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;\">Hypothesize</div>\n          <div style=\"font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 4px;\">\"What if I disable graph expansion and increase top_k instead?\"</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"card\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-green); padding: 20px 24px;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 15px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-green); min-width: 28px;\">3</div>\n        <div>\n          <div style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;\">Act</div>\n          <div style=\"font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 4px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 16px; color: var(--accent-green);\">config_set rag.graph_expansion_depth = 0</span>. Hot-reload. No restart.</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"card\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-purple); padding: 20px 24px;\">",
